  <p>Make sure you end each tag with a semicolon. It's ok to use spaces in or between the tags.</p>
  <p>There are lots of online generators for creating shapes and patterns. For example, <a href="https://appearate.azurewebsites.net/Plaid" target="_blank">this one makes plaid.</a></p>
