<p>The plaid pattern is made by layering gradients over one another.</p>
<h2>CSS is powerful and you could use it to mess up the site pretty bad.</h2>
<p>We're trying to prevent you from doing this so we don't have to remove this feature. If you find any security problems please let us know so we can continue to allow custom CSS.</p>
<p>There are lots of other properties you can change to create complex effects. <a href="https://www.w3schools.com/css/default.asp" target="_blank">Check out W3Schools for more info.</a></p>
